OL,3,CTime for clarity regarding future of
OL,4,CFreeview
OL,6,GIf a story or rumour is not denied
OL,7,Gquickly it can quickly grow arms and
OL,8,Glegs.
OL,10,FIt is time for the government to make
OL,11,Fit clear that Freeview is not going
OL,12,Fanywhere anytime soon.
OL,14,FOtherwise the fear could build up.
OL,15,FHysterical press stories could begin.
OL,17,FAnd, worst of all, the elderly and
OL,18,Fdisadvantaged could be left anxious or
OL,19,Fexploited by those seeking to make a
OL,20,Ffast buck.
