OL,3,CTime for clarity regarding future of
OL,4,CFreeview
OL,6,FThere are parallels. Some people
OL,7,Fscarcely use hard cash now ` others
OL,8,Fare still dependent on it. Nobody in
OL,9,Fthe mainstream wants to abolish notes
OL,10,Fand coins.
OL,12,FSwitching off the public service
OL,13,Fmultiplexes ` which carry BBC, ITV and
OL,14,FChannel 4 services together with
OL,15,FChannel 5 ` should only be
OL,16,Fcontemplated once Freeview accounts
OL,17,Ffor a small share of free viewing.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/7
