OL,3,CTime for clarity regarding future of
OL,4,CFreeview
OL,6,FI would suggest it can only be
OL,7,Fconsidered once most people who don't
OL,8,Fwant pay TV have migrated naturally to
OL,9,FFreely leaving Freeview with barely 20
OL,10,F` 25% of free viewing.
OL,12,FThat day could be a long way off.
OL,14,FAnd even then plenty of notice would
OL,15,Fneed to be given. Probably 5 years.
OL,17,FThe one thing which should be
OL,18,Fdiscussed now is whether some small
OL,19,Frelay transmitters are still necessary.
