OL,3,CTime for clarity regarding future of
OL,4,CFreeview
OL,6,FMost of the transmitters built after
OL,7,Fthe late-70s were designed to deal
OL,8,Fwith localised reception issues ` bad
OL,9,Fghosting or dips in the signal ` or
OL,10,Fexamples of communities getting the
OL,11,F"wrong" region, especially in rural
OL,12,Fparts of Scotland and Wales.
OL,14,FIn practice some of those transmitters
OL,15,Fmay be little used now or the problem
OL,16,Fthey sought to solve may not be a
OL,17,Fpractical issue for digital viewers.
OL,19,FAny move to reduce coverage would need
OL,20,Fcareful consideration and need
OL,21,Fapproval from Ofcom.
